        "mapping": {
          "B": "cuisine:earthen_basin",
          "P": "minecraft:piston[facing=down,extended=false]"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "crafting",
      "recipe": "cuisine:wooden_basin",
      "text": "木盆只有一种版本：橡木纹理的木盆。木盆只能用于$(em)接触$()和$(em)挤压$()，无法用于$(em)加热$()。"
    },
    {
